message.entry: Structure field must contain logical scalar.
Unknown field in the structure array input. Valid field names are: "LT", "UT", "UHESS", "SYM", "POSDEF", "RECT", and "TRANSA".
First and second arguments must be single or double.
First and second arguments must be 2-D.
Linsolve is not supported for sparse inputs.
Third argument must be a structure array.
